headline: Prediction: 2 Stocks That Will Be Worth More Than AGNC Investment 10 Years From Now
summary: Over the past decade, AGNC Investment has had a very clear, downward dividend trend.  Retail-focused Federal Realty is a Dividend King that uses both internal and external growth levers.  Rexford Industrial is a hyper-focused industrial REIT, but it has skills that set it apart from its competitors.
